txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="2" name="Rectangle 1"/><p:cNvSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="425223" y="1091690"/><a:ext cx="8213952" cy="4247317"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr wrap="square"><a:spAutoFit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/><a:t>Look for entitlements lying with your business and not uploaded onto EARL. For entitlements not present, remove the unused </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0" smtClean="0"/><a:t>software</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" i="1" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/><a:t>We must respond diligently in the expected timeframes, the levels of flexibility will be short and based on approved exceptions</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/><a:t>If you don’t find the proof of entitlement for a product, don’t waste your time trying to find it beyond acceptable efforts and perform remediation.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/><a:t>Speed up the procurement process, push for the PO to be approved and the invoice to be sent to you by the vendor, as otherwise will take weeks to happen.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="457200" indent="-457200" eaLnBrk="1" hangingPunct="1"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buFont typeface="GE Inspira" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buAutoNum type="arabicPeriod"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2000" dirty="0"/><a:t>As soon as you get the invoice, upload it into EARL. Don’t wait.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree><p:extLst><p:ext uri="{BB962C8B-B14F-4D97-AF65-F5344CB8AC3E}"><p14:creationId xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main" val="2963230521"/></p:ext></p:extLst></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr><p:timing><p:tnLst><p:par><p:cTn id="1" dur="indefinite" restart="never" nodeType="tmRoot"/></p:par></p:tnLst></p:timing></p:sld>